03:11.240 --> 03:11.900
Betul juga.

03:13.800 --> 03:15.200
Adakah kamu kawan You Li?

03:15.800 --> 03:16.150
Ya.

03:16.560 --> 03:17.120
Kami perlu dapatkan

03:17.120 --> 03:18.450
